<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Pneumanosis — AI-Powered Chest X-Ray Triage</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;700;800&family=Outfit:wght@400;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  :root {
    --cyan: #00e5ff;
    --lime: #76ff03;
    --orange: #ff6e40;
    --purple: #ab47bc;
    --rose: #ff4081;
    --bg-deep: #030810;
    --bg-mid: #060e18;
    --bg-light: #0a1929;
    --text-primary: #e0e0e0;
    --text-muted: #90a4ae;
    --text-dim: #546e7a;
    --text-faint: #78909c;
    --glass-bg: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    --glass-border: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    --mono: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    --sans: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 50%, var(--bg-light) 0%, var(--bg-mid) 50%, var(--bg-deep) 100%);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    min-height: 100vh;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* ── particles ── */
  .particles { position: fixed; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; z-index: 0; }
  .particle { position: absolute; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(0,229,255,0.2); }

  /* ── grid overlay ── */
  .grid-overlay {
    position: fixed; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(0,229,255,0.015) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,229,255,0.015) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 60px 60px;
  }

  /* ── vignette ── */
  .vignette {
    position: fixed; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; z-index: 1;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, transparent 40%, rgba(3,8,16,0.7) 100%);
  }

  /* ── top bar ── */
  .topbar {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 50;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 16px 28px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(6,14,24,0.95) 0%, transparent 100%);
  }
  .topbar-logo { font: 800 13px/1 var(--mono); letter-spacing: 4px; color: var(--cyan); }
  .topbar-right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; }
  .btn-pause {
    background: none; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    color: var(--text-muted); padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 20px;
    font: 12px var(--mono); cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-pause:hover { border-color: var(--cyan); color: var(--cyan); }
  .slide-counter { font: 12px var(--mono); color: var(--text-dim); }
  .timer-display { font: 700 12px var(--mono); color: var(--cyan); opacity: 0.7; }

  /* ── slides wrapper ── */
  .slides-viewport {
    position: relative; z-index: 10;
    max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 64px 28px 48px;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }
  .slide {
    display: none; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 16px;
    width: 100%; max-height: calc(100vh - 100px); overflow-y: auto;
    opacity: 0; transform: translateY(40px);
    transition: opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1), transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1);
  }
  .slide.active { display: flex; }
  .slide::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
  .slide { scrollbar-width: none; }
  .slide.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

  /* ── shared ── */
  .tag {
    font: 700 10px/1 var(--mono);
    letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cyan); padding: 5px 14px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.15);
    border-radius: 20px; background: rgba(0,229,255,0.04);
  }
  .heading {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem);
    font-weight: 800; text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.15; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .body-text { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; text-align: center; }
  .glass {
    background: var(--glass-bg); border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    border-radius: 12px; backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  }
  .accent-line {
    width: 48px; height: 3px; border-radius: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--cyan), var(--lime));
  }

  /* ── title slide ── */
  .title-main {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 7vw, 5.5rem);
    font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -0.03em; line-height: 1;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0e0e0 0%, var(--cyan) 50%, var(--lime) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text; text-align: center;
  }
  .title-sub {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.2vw, 1.4rem);
    color: var(--text-muted); max-width: 600px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .title-detail {
    font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 6px; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cyan); font-weight: 600;
  }
  .title-tracks {
    display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .title-track {
    font: 600 11px var(--mono); color: var(--text-dim);
    padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
  }

  /* ── stats row ── */
  .stats-row { display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }
  .stat-card { padding: 18px 28px; text-align: center; min-width: 140px; }
  .stat-value { font: 900 clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2.2rem)/1 var(--mono); color: var(--cyan); }
  .stat-label { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 6px; line-height: 1.4; }
  .source { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim); font-style: italic; }

  /* ── solution cards ── */
  .cards-row { display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; width: 100%; }
  .sol-card {
    padding: 20px 20px; max-width: 270px; flex: 1 1 220px;
    border-top: 2px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.3);
  }
  .sol-card .icon { font-size: 26px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .sol-card h3 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .sol-card p { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.5; }

  /* ── image showcase ── */
  .img-showcase {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 860px;
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 14px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.2);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px -10px rgba(0,229,255,0.15);
    transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1), box-shadow 0.4s ease;
    background: var(--bg-deep);
  }
  .img-showcase:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.02);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 50px -5px rgba(0,229,255,0.3);
    border-color: rgba(0,229,255,0.5);
  }
  .img-showcase img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  .img-caption {
    font: 600 13px var(--mono);
    color: var(--lime);
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* ── pipeline ── */
  .pipeline { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2px; max-width: 680px; width: 100%; }
  .pipe-step { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; padding: 12px 18px; }
  .pipe-num { font: 900 22px/1 var(--mono); color: rgba(0,229,255,0.2); min-width: 36px; }
  .pipe-name { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; }
  .pipe-desc { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-faint); margin-top: 2px; }

  /* ── architecture ── */
  .arch-layers { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; max-width: 680px; width: 100%; }
  .arch-layer { padding: 14px 18px; }
  .arch-layer-name { font: 800 11px/1 var(--mono); letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .arch-pills { display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .arch-pill {
    font-size: 12px; color: #b0bec5; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }

  /* ── demo box ── */
  .demo-box { padding: 32px 30px; max-width: 540px; width: 100%; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .demo-step {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px;
    padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    position: relative; z-index: 2;
  }
  .demo-step:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .demo-num {
    width: 26px; height: 26px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(0,229,255,0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.3);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font: 800 12px var(--mono); color: var(--cyan); flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .demo-step span { font-size: 14px; color: #cfd8dc; }

  /* ── impact ── */
  .impact-row { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }
  .impact-card {
    padding: 20px 28px; text-align: center; min-width: 160px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(118,255,3,0.3);
  }
  .impact-icon { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .impact-value { font: 900 clamp(1.6rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem)/1 var(--mono); color: var(--lime); }
  .impact-label { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 6px; line-height: 1.4; }

  /* ── learning grid ── */
  .learn-grid { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; max-width: 720px; }
  .learn-card {
    padding: 18px 18px; flex: 1 1 200px; max-width: 230px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--cyan);
  }
  .learn-card h4 { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .learn-card p { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.5; }
  .learn-card.orange { border-left-color: var(--orange); }
  .learn-card.lime { border-left-color: var(--lime); }

  /* ── roadmap ── */
  .roadmap { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; max-width: 560px; width: 100%; }
  .roadmap-item {
    display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: flex-start; padding: 18px 22px;
  }
  .roadmap-phase {
    font: 800 11px var(--mono); letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
    min-width: 64px; padding-top: 2px;
  }
  .roadmap-item h4 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .roadmap-item p { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.5; }

  /* ── team ── */
  .team-cta {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem);
    font-weight: 800; text-align: center; line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .team-links { display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }
  .team-link {
    font: 13px var(--mono); color: var(--cyan);
    padding: 8px 20px; border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.3); border-radius: 24px;
    transition: all 0.2s; text-decoration: none;
  }
  .team-link:hover { background: rgba(0,229,255,0.08); }

  /* ── conditions table ── */
  .conditions-table { max-width: 620px; width: 100%; border-collapse: separate; border-spacing: 0 4px; }
  .conditions-table th {
    font: 700 10px var(--mono); letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-dim); text-align: left; padding: 6px 14px;
  }
  .conditions-table td {
    padding: 10px 14px; font-size: 13px;
    background: var(--glass-bg); border-top: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
  }
  .conditions-table tr td:first-child { border-left: 1px solid var(--glass-border); border-radius: 8px 0 0 8px; }
  .conditions-table tr td:last-child { border-right: 1px solid var(--glass-border); border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; }
  .tier-badge {
    font: 800 12px var(--mono); padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 12px; display: inline-block;
  }
  .tier-2 { background: rgba(255,110,64,0.15); color: var(--orange); border: 1px solid rgba(255,110,64,0.3); }
  .tier-3 { background: rgba(255,64,129,0.12); color: var(--rose); border: 1px solid rgba(255,64,129,0.25); }
  .tier-4 { background: rgba(0,229,255,0.1); color: var(--cyan); border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.25); }
  .urgency-text { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); }

  /* ── social impact ── */
  .impact-points { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; max-width: 600px; width: 100%; }
  .impact-point { display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: flex-start; padding: 14px 18px; }
  .impact-bullet {
    width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0;
    background: rgba(118,255,3,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(118,255,3,0.2);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 14px;
  }
  .impact-point h4 { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .impact-point p { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.5; }

  /* ── nav dots ── */
  .dots {
    position: fixed; bottom: 20px; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 50;
    display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 6px;
  }
  .dot {
    width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 4px; border: none; cursor: pointer;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .dot.active { width: 24px; background: var(--cyan); animation: pulse 2s infinite; }

  /* ── arrows ── */
  .arrow {
    position: fixed; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    color: var(--text-faint); width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 50%;
    font-size: 18px; cursor: pointer; z-index: 50;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .arrow:hover { border-color: var(--cyan); color: var(--cyan); }
  .arrow-left { left: 16px; }
  .arrow-right { right: 16px; }

  /* ── progress bar ── */
  .progress-track {
    position: fixed; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 3px; z-index: 100; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  }
  .progress-fill {
    height: 100%; width: 0%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--cyan), var(--lime));
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(0,229,255,0.5);
  }
  .progress-fill.animating { animation: progressFill var(--autoplay-ms) linear forwards; }

  /* ── stagger animations ── */
  .stagger > * { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); transition: opacity 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease; }
  .slide.visible .stagger > *:nth-child(1) { opacity:1; transform:none; transition-delay:0.15s; }
  .slide.visible .stagger > *:nth-child(2) { opacity:1; transform:none; transition-delay:0.27s; }
  .slide.visible .stagger > *:nth-child(3) { opacity:1; transform:none; transition-delay:0.39s; }
  .slide.visible .stagger > *:nth-child(4) { opacity:1; transform:none; transition-delay:0.51s; }
  .slide.visible .stagger > *:nth-child(5) { opacity:1; transform:none; transition-delay:0.63s; }
  .slide.visible .stagger > *:nth-child(6) { opacity:1; transform:none; transition-delay:0.75s; }
  .slide.visible .stagger > *:nth-child(7) { opacity:1; transform:none; transition-delay:0.87s; }
  .slide.visible .stagger > *:nth-child(8) { opacity:1; transform:none; transition-delay:0.99s; }

  .stagger-right > * { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-24px); transition: opacity 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease; }
  .slide.visible .stagger-right > *:nth-child(1) { opacity:1; transform:none; transition-delay:0.2s; }
  .slide.visible .stagger-right > *:nth-child(2) { opacity:1; transform:none; transition-delay:0.32s; }
  .slide.visible .stagger-right > *:nth-child(3) { opacity:1; transform:none; transition-delay:0.44s; }
  .slide.visible .stagger-right > *:nth-child(4) { opacity:1; transform:none; transition-delay:0.56s; }
  .slide.visible .stagger-right > *:nth-child(5) { opacity:1; transform:none; transition-delay:0.68s; }
  .slide.visible .stagger-right > *:nth-child(6) { opacity:1; transform:none; transition-delay:0.80s; }

  /* ── keyframes ── */
  @keyframes floatUp {
    0% { transform: translateY(100vh) scale(0); opacity: 0; }
    10% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    90% { opacity: 0.6; }
    100% { transform: translateY(-100vh) scale(0.5); opacity: 0; }
  }
  @keyframes progressFill { from { width: 0%; } to { width: 100%; } }
  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(0,229,255,0.3); }
    50% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(0,229,255,0); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .arrow { display: none; }
    .slides-viewport { padding: 56px 16px 44px; }
    .img-showcase { max-width: 100%; }
    .conditions-table { font-size: 12px; }
    .conditions-table td { padding: 10px 10px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="particles" id="particles"></div>
<div class="grid-overlay"></div>
<div class="vignette"></div>

<div class="topbar">
  <div class="topbar-logo">PNEUMANOSIS</div>
  <div class="topbar-right">
    <span class="timer-display" id="timerDisplay">0:00 / 3:02</span>
    <button class="btn-pause" id="btnPause">❚❚ PAUSE</button>
    <span class="slide-counter" id="counter">01 / 14</span>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="slides-viewport">

  <!-- ════════════ SLIDE 1 — TITLE ════════════ -->
  <div class="slide active" data-index="0">
    <span class="tag">REVOLUTIONUC 2026</span>
    <h1 class="title-main">PNEUMANOSIS</h1>
    <p class="title-sub">Chest X-Ray Triage Co-Pilot for Health Professionals</p>
    <p class="title-detail">Prioritize · Detect · Manage</p>
    <div class="title-tracks">
      <span class="title-track">MobileNetV3-Small · 0.87 AUC</span>
      <span class="title-track">Not a Replacement — A Co-Pilot</span>
      <span class="title-track">Educational Purposes Only</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ════════════ SLIDE 2 — THE PROBLEM ════════════ -->
  <div class="slide" data-index="1">
    <span class="tag">THE PROBLEM</span>
    <h2 class="heading">Radiologists Are Drowning</h2>
    <div class="stats-row stagger">
      <div class="stat-card glass">
        <div class="stat-value">44–65%</div>
        <div class="stat-label">of radiologists<br>report burnout</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card glass">
        <div class="stat-value">80%</div>
        <div class="stat-label">workload growth<br>2009–2020</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card glass">
        <div class="stat-value">130 days</div>
        <div class="stat-label">avg. time to fill a<br>rural radiology position</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="body-text" style="max-width:660px">Workload surged with no matching increase in positions. Critical chest X-ray findings like edema, consolidation, and pleural effusion get buried in first-come-first-serve queues — costing time and risking patient outcomes.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- ════════════ SLIDE 3 — OUR SOLUTION ════════════ -->
  <div class="slide" data-index="2">
    <span class="tag">OUR SOLUTION</span>
    <h2 class="heading">A Co-Pilot, Not a Replacement</h2>
    <div class="cards-row stagger">
      <div class="sol-card glass">
        <div class="icon">🫁</div>
        <h3>5-Condition Detection</h3>
        <p>MobileNetV3-Small trained on CheXpert (0.87 AUC) with real-time inference at ~100–125ms on CPU. 50% confidence threshold.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="sol-card glass">
        <div class="icon">🚦</div>
        <h3>STAT / PRIORITY / ROUTINE</h3>
        <p>Patients ranked using standard radiology PACS terminology. All STAT cases surface above PRIORITY, above ROUTINE — tier-first clinical sorting.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="sol-card glass">
        <div class="icon">📋</div>
        <h3>Full Patient Management</h3>
        <p>Save, search, flag, delete, and export patient records. Confirm, dismiss, or flag findings for second opinion — all via API.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ════════════ SLIDE 4 — DASHBOARD: TRIAGE QUEUE ════════════ -->
  <div class="slide" data-index="3">
    <span class="tag">DASHBOARD</span>
    <h2 class="heading">The Triage Queue</h2>
    <div class="stagger" style="width: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;">
      <div class="img-showcase">
        <img src="patientview.png" alt="Pneumanosis Triage Queue showing patients sorted by STAT, PRIORITY, ROUTINE tiers">
      </div>
      <div class="img-caption">Landing Page — Stats Cards · Priority Donut Chart · Search · Filter · Export CSV</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ════════════ SLIDE 5 — DASHBOARD: PATIENT DETAIL ════════════ -->
  <div class="slide" data-index="4">
    <span class="tag">PATIENT DETAIL</span>
    <h2 class="heading">3-Panel Clinical Layout</h2>
    <div class="stagger" style="width: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;">
      <div class="img-showcase">
        <img src="TriageQueue.png" alt="Pneumanosis Patient Detail with 3-panel layout showing patient list, X-ray with findings, and patient info">
